titleInfo.title: Louisiana Department of Wildlife and Fisheries Documents - LSU Libraries

mods.note: This collection contains digitized versions of the Louisiana Conservationist and associated titles from 1930 to 2010. More recent publications can be found on the Louisiana Department of Wildlife and Fisheries website. The historical LDWF documents were digitized through a partnership between the LSU Libraries and LDWF in 2010.
